The non-obvious thing that cracked it.
```

## Communication

- Be direct — lead with the formula or code, explain after
- Show the actual Excel formula, not a description of it
- State assumptions explicitly when data is ambiguous
- After generating a file: state path, sheet names, and what each contains
- Russian labels in formulas and headers are fine — use them when the user does
